I‚Äôm going to demand civility of those I work with, of Hoosier legislators of both parties, and of myself.

Like many of you here today, I believe a key to achieving goals is focus. That‚Äôs why, as Governor, I‚Äôm focusing on five pillars I believe we need to take Indiana to the Next Level.
My point is, you can‚Äôt obey the Boy Scout Law and be uncivil. It‚Äôs impossible.

The essence of the Boy Scouts: they develop heroes & leaders by instilling the character & values that are the wellsprings of leadership.
